Okay, first of all,
let me just say,

10:21.888 --> 10:24.355
I think we're all concerned

10:24.357 --> 10:26.324
about the drought in California.

10:26.326 --> 10:27.358
I haven't showered in six days.

10:27.360 --> 10:29.060
Oh, so you're saying
you want to fight.

10:29.062 --> 10:31.529
That's a huge
leap in logic.

10:31.531 --> 10:33.064
You want to fight?
Yeah.

10:33.066 --> 10:34.499
I'll fight you and then
I'll take a hot shower,

10:34.501 --> 10:36.234
you s-sandy lizard man.

10:36.236 --> 10:38.202
Let's do this. Totally, totally,
totally, totally, totally.

10:38.204 --> 10:39.704
Yeah, let's fight these guys, Nick.
Yeah, totally.

10:39.706 --> 10:41.239
We're gonna
fight these guys.

10:41.241 --> 10:44.008
Uh, but not indoors.

10:44.010 --> 10:45.510
