Yeah, we're gonna urinate
and then we're gonna do this.

11:02.762 --> 11:04.195
Yeah.

11:04.197 --> 11:05.997
Uh, is there a key?
Do I need a key to the restroom?

11:11.604 --> 11:14.205
Ooh, God, I hope I get to
kick somebody in the head.

11:14.207 --> 11:15.440
What are you doing
with that window?

11:15.442 --> 11:17.909
You letting a bee out?
That's dope, man.

11:17.911 --> 11:20.411
N-N-N-N-N-No. We're escaping. We're
