never had to pay for a ham.

11:25.919 --> 11:27.752
We're escaping?
How-how is that butch, Nick?

11:27.754 --> 11:29.220
Enough with the butch stuff,
Schmidt.

11:29.222 --> 11:31.089
You got to let
this Toby thing go.

11:31.091 --> 11:33.624
If I freaked out every time
somebody yelled at me, I...

11:33.626 --> 11:35.226
It's not because
I got yelled at.

11:35.228 --> 11:37.395
It's because I got yelled at
in front of Cece.

11:37.397 --> 11:40.431
You know, I know she
can handle herself,

11:40.433 --> 11:42.934
but I need to prove to myself
that I can defend her

11:42.936 --> 11:45.403
from the lunatic pagans
of the world.

11:45.405 --> 11:46.604
Because if I can't,

11:46.606 --> 11:48.606
what kind of husband
am I going to be?

11:48.608 --> 11:50.608
I understand if
you don't want

11:50.610 --> 11:52.410
any part of this,

11:52.412 --> 11:54.245
but this is something
I have to do.

11:54.247 --> 11:57.682
For me.

12:00.086 --> 12:02.086
(sighs)

12:02.088 --> 12:04.155
Okay. I'm in.

12:04.157 --> 12:06.290
If you got to do it,
then I got your back.

12:06.292 --> 12:07.592
There's two of them,
there's two of us.

12:07.594 --> 12:08.893
We can do this.

12:10.997 --> 12:12.997
They got a lot of
rings, Schmidty.

12:25.845 --> 12:27.145
We are so outnumbered.
So outnumbered.

12:27.147 --> 12:28.246
We're not going
to win this fight.

12:29.616 --> 12:31.983
That's a little boy
over there.

12:31.985 --> 12:33.317
Where'd that little
boy come from?

12:33.319 --> 12:35.153
