I'm Schmidt.

13:18.364 --> 13:19.664
In case you're
wondering what my n...

13:19.666 --> 13:20.731
...what my name is,
it's Schmidt.

13:20.733 --> 13:21.832
Schmidt!

13:21.834 --> 13:23.668
This is Nick!
Nick! Schmidt!

13:23.670 --> 13:26.904
You know what
would be a good plan?

13:26.906 --> 13:29.707
You get a job at
a Raisin Bran factory, right?

13:29.709 --> 13:31.008
You start stealing

13:31.010 --> 13:33.044
all of the raisins, okay?
You follow?

13:33.046 --> 13:34.512
Then you hydrate those raisins

13:34.514 --> 13:36.247
