13:38.017 --> 13:40.918
There's no overhead, and you
make you a very rich man.

13:40.920 --> 13:42.753
That's right, Wilson.

13:42.755 --> 13:44.422
You have surrendered
to the night.

13:44.424 --> 13:46.057
I'm Wilson.

13:46.059 --> 13:47.592
Schmidt!
Yeah, I'm Schmidt!

13:48.228 --> 13:49.560
My babies.

13:49.562 --> 13:51.862
Ain't nobody gonna
touch my babies.

13:51.864 --> 13:53.431
(whooping)

13:53.433 --> 13:54.765
Knuckle up!

13:54.767 --> 13:56.234
Yeah, I'm feeling dangerous!
No, no, no.

13:56.236 --> 13:57.935
Winston. Winston. No.
Uh-huh!

13:57.937 --> 13:59.437
I ain't got no phone.
I ain't got no Aly.

13:59.439 --> 14:00.571
No, no, no, no, no, no
no, no, no, no, no.

