with my desert queen.

20:53.085 --> 20:56.754
Besides, there's nothing
for me in the city.

20:56.756 --> 20:59.256
Wait a second. Don't you
have two kids? Yeah.

20:59.258 --> 21:00.758
I'll be back Sunday.

21:00.760 --> 21:01.925
I got to pick them up
from swim camp.

21:01.927 --> 21:03.427
Good luck, fellas.

21:13.472 --> 21:15.639
We should go now.
Let's do it.

21:15.641 --> 21:17.975
We're men.
ALL: Men!

21:17.977 --> 21:19.276
Let's ride.
Let's ride.

21:19.278 --> 21:20.778
Let's ride. Let's ride.

21:20.780 --> 21:23.781
Yeah, yeah, yeah.
No, no, no, no. I'm good.

21:23.783 --> 21:24.948
Men. We're men.

21:24.950 --> 21:26.383
Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Sit, sit, sit.

21:26.385 --> 21:28.552
♪ I've got
the eye of the tiger ♪

21:28.554 --> 21:29.987
♪ A fighter ♪

21:29.989 --> 21:31.288
Best bachelor
party ever, Nick!

